oreground h-10 px-4 py-2\" href=\"https://app.saga.co.id\">Masuk</a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 px-4 py-2\" href=\"https://app.saga.co.id\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap mr-2 h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg>Daftar Sekarang</a></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><section class=\"py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30 overflow-hidden relative\"><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 px-4 py-1 text-primary border-primary\">Tentang Kami</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight\">Dari Pengalaman Nyata, <br/><span class=\"text-primary\">Untuk Solusi Nyata</span></h1><p class=\"text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed\">Saga hadir bukan sekadar sebagai pembuat aplikasi, tapi sebagai partner transformasi digital untuk komunitas dan bisnis Anda.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10\"></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-background\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-4\">Perjalanan Kami</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-lg\">Bagaimana sebuah masalah kecil melahirkan solusi besar.</p></div><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto relative\"><div class=\"absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-border -translate-x-1/2 hidden md:block\"></div><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start relative md:flex-row-reverse\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-background border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 hidden md:flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-all md:text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 md:flex-row\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Awal Mula</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold tracking-tight text-xl\">Pengalaman sebagai Pengurus</h3></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Berawal dari pengalaman pribadi menjadi pengurus komunitas. Mengelola iuran dan data warga secara manual ternyata sangat melelahkan dan rentan kesalahan.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 hidden md:block\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start relative \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-background border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 hidden md:flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-all md:text-right\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 md:flex-row-reverse\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search w-5 h-5\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle><path d=\"m21 21-4.3-4.3\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Masalah Utama</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold tracking-tight text-xl\">Krisis Transparansi</h3></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Kami menemukan fakta mengejutkan: Hanya 36% warga yang sadar akan pentingnya konfirmasi digital. Hal ini menyebabkan ketidakcocokan data dan rasa saling curiga antar warga.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 hidden md:block\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start relative md:flex-row-reverse\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-background border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 hidden md:flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-all md:text-left\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 md:flex-row\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb w-5 h-5\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Solusi Lahir</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold tracking-tight text-xl\">Saga &amp; Sahabat Warga</h3></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Kami mendirikan Saga dengan misi membantu bisnis dan komunitas bertransformasi digital. Sahabat Warga lahir sebagai solusi transparansi keuangan lingkungan.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 hidden md:block\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start relative \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-8 h-8 bg-background border-2 border-primary rounded-full z-10 hidden md:flex items-center justify-center\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border bg-card text-card-foreground shadow-sm h-full hover:shadow-lg transition-all md:text-right\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-1.5 p-6\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 md:flex-row-reverse\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up w-5 h-5\"><polyline points=\"22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17\"></polyline><polyline points=\"16 7 22 7 22 13\"></polyline></svg></div><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\">Masa Depan</div></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold tracking-tight text-xl\">Pertumbuhan Bersama</h3></div><div class=\"p-6 pt-0\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Kini Saga fokus membantu masyarakat dan bisnis untuk tumbuh (growth) melalui adaptasi teknologi yang tepat guna dan mudah digunakan.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 hidden md:block\"></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-muted/30\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex-1 relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-200 to-gray-300 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl relative group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center bg-muted\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-users w-24 h-24 text-muted-foreground/30\"><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87\"></path><path d=\"M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border-[10px] border-background/30 rounded-2xl z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl -z-10\"></div><div class=\"absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-400/10 rounded-full blur-2xl -z-10\"></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent hover:bg-primary/80 bg-primary text-primary-foreground\">Founder Profile</div><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold\">Dede Kurnihawan</h2><p class=\"text-lg font-medium text-primary\">Founder &amp; CEO Saga</p><blockquote class=\"border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 italic text-muted-foreground text-lg\">&quot;Permasalahan terbesar dalam pengelolaan komunitas bukan pada uangnya, tapi pada <span class=\"text-foreground font-semibold\">kepercayaan</span>. Transparansi adalah kunci untuk membangun kepercayaan tersebut.&quot;</blockquote><div class=\"space-y-4 pt-4\"><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Berpengalaman langsung sebagai pengurus lingkungan, Dede merasakan betapa sulitnya menjaga akuntabilitas dengan metode manual. Ia menemukan bahwa hanya 36% warga yang sadar akan pentingnya konfirmasi digital, menciptakan celah transparansi yang besar.</p><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Melalui Saga, Dede bertekad membantu bisnis dan komunitas untuk tidak hanya mendigitalkan proses, tetapi juga <span class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">bertumbuh (growth)</span> melalui adaptasi teknologi yang manusiawi.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6\"><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 px-4 py-2\" href=\"https://linkedin.com/in/dedekurnihawan\">Lihat Profil Profesional <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 bg-background\"><div class=\"container text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-12\">Nilai-Nilai Kami</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground bg-primary/5 border-none shadow-none\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-background rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Transparansi</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Keterbukaan adalah fondasi dari setiap solusi yang kami bangun.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground bg-primary/5 border-none shadow-none\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-background rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Pertumbuhan</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Kami membantu partner kami untuk tumbuh, bukan sekadar bertahan.</p></div></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border text-card-foreground bg-primary/5 border-none shadow-none\"><div class=\"p-6 pt-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-background rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-6 h-6\"><path d=\"M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">Empati</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Solusi kami lahir dari pemahaman mendalam akan masalah pengguna.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-center\"><div class=\"container\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Siap Bertransformasi Bersama Saga?</h2><div class=\"flex justify-center gap-4\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80 h-11 rounded-md px-8\" href=\"/\">Pelajari Produk Kami</a></div></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-background border-t pt-16 pb-8\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4 relative\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-12 md:gap-16 mb-16 md:mb-20\"><div class=\"max-w-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 shrink-0 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-primary/10\"><img alt=\"Sahabat Warga Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-8 h-8 object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Ficon.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Ficon.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Ficon.png&amp;w=64&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Solusi praktis untuk mengelola, memantau, dan mengingatkan iuran digital dengan mudah.</p></div><div class=\"border-t border-border pt-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><img alt=\"Terdaftar PSE Kominfo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-20 object-contain grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fpse.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Terdaftar PSE</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-16 w-full md:w-auto\"><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-6 text-lg text-foreground relative inline-block\">Produk<span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-12 h-1 bg-primary rounded-full\"></span></h4><ul class=\"space-y-4\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"/#features\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg>Fitur</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"/#pricing\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg>Harga</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"/docs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg>Dokumentasi</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground hover:text-primary transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group\" href=\"#\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg>Server Status</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-6 text-lg text-foreground relative inline-block\">Perusahaan<span class=\"abso